Deltagrid
=========

Deltagrid (dgrid for short) is an attempt to create an open-source software 
for provisioning, configuration management, and application-deployment 
in diverse android + SBC (single board computers) + server linux environments 
focused primary on custom/experimental installations. 

Install
=======

See INSTALL file.

TLDR
=======
dgrid as system functions as a group of dgrid software installations called 
nodes. Node can be installed on any compatible host, multiple nodes can
be installed under same user. Node communicate between themselves using 
ssh (mostly).
